trans-unit.target: TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_SEQ_00<tab>Oswell needs your help to locate a misplaced shipment.
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_SEQ_01<tab>Oswell cannot locate three crates scheduled for transport to the East Aldenard Trading Company. Search Scorpion Crossing for the missing crates.
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_SEQ_02<tab>You have found the three misplaced crates. Present them to Oswell and put his mind at ease.
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_SEQ_03<tab>Oswell thanks you for your assistance in locating the crates. Alas, despite your efforts, the overworked man will not find respite from his work any time soon.
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_OSWELL_001<tab>You've time to spare, don't you? Make yourself useful and help me find my missing crates!

TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_OSWELL_002<tab>The manifest clearly states that three crates bound for the East Aldenard Trading Company were included in the latest shipment from Vesper Bay, but I can't seem to find the bloody things.
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_OSWELL_003<tab>They ought to be around here somewhere, but I can't waste any more time looking. If you find the crates, bring them to me!
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_OSWELL_011<tab>Great job, friend! These will make the next wagon thanks to you!
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_OSWELL_012<tab>The shipments never stop coming, day in and day out. Just keeping track of everything is enough to give me migraines.
TEXT_SUBWIL030_00222_OSWELL_013<tab>Business is good, true, but what use is money if you haven't the time to spend it? I haven't downed a pint with friends in weeks!
